			<div id="post-3818" class="post-3818 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-food category-random tag-olive-oil">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://chocolateandcarrots.com/2011/04/you-need-some-of-this" title="Permalink to You need some of this." rel="bookmark">You need some of this.</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://chocolateandcarrots.com/2011/04/you-need-some-of-this" title="6:31 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">April 5, 2011</span></a> <span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://chocolateandcarrots.com/author/caroline" title="View all posts by caroline">caroline</a></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<p><em><strong>Olive oil</strong>.</em></p>
<p>And have you ever pondered why people from the Mediterranean live so long and are so healthy?</p>
<p>Your heart will thank you for some olive oil.</p>
<p>Only in moderation&#8230;like everything else, well, except <strong>chocolate</strong> and <strong>peanut butter</strong>.</p>
<p>I consume way over moderation. I love me some chocolate and peanut butter! <img src='http://chocolateandcarrots.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif' alt=':-D' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Anyway&#8230;just some fun with video and iMovie. Enjoy this 20 second movie! <img src='http://chocolateandcarrots.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':-)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
