						<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://chocolateandcarrots.com/category/food/dessert/cookie" title="View all posts in cookie" rel="category tag">cookie</a>, <a href="http://chocolateandcarrots.com/category/food/dessert" title="View all posts in dessert" rel="category tag">dessert</a>, <a href="http://chocolateandcarrots.com/category/food" title="View all posts in food" rel="category tag">food</a>					</span>
